<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="train-n">train <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /treɪn/    美 /treɪn/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>火车：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>travel <strong>by train</strong> 
坐火车旅行</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>长列；队列：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a long train of visitors before the monument 
纪念碑前长长的参观队伍</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>系列：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>A train of</strong> nice recollections runs across my mind when speaking about my college years. 
一说起大学时代，我的脑中就闪过一串美好的回忆。</p></div></div>